process.name: Get Active Tokens by Multiple Criteria

processVariable.name: tokenDetails

TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlString select LBI.BPD_NAME as BPDName, LBI.INSTANCE_NAME as instanceName, LBI.BPD_REF as BPDRefID, lbsc.NAME as executionStatus, LBI.TIP as isTip, LBI.CREATE_DATETIME as createdDateTime, lt.TASK_ID as TaskID, LP."NAME" as ApplicationName, LUX.USER_NAME as StartedByUser, LUGX.DESCRIPTION as groupName, LT.SUBJECT as TaskSubject, LT.ACTIVITY_NAME as ActivityName, LT.BPD_INSTANCE_ID as InstanceID, LTSC."NAME" as TaskStatus from lsw_project lp, lsw_snapshot ls, lsw_usr_xref lux, lsw_task lt, LSW_TASK_STATUS_CODES ltsc, lsw_usr_grp_xref lugx, lsw_bpd_instance lbi, LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES lbsc where lp.project_id = ls.PROJECT_ID and lt.user_id = lux.user_id(+) and LT.snapshot_id = LS.SNAPSHOT_ID and LTSC.STATUS_VALUE = LT.STATUS and LT."GROUP_ID" = LUGX."GROUP_ID"(+) and LBI.bpd_instance_id = LT.BPD_INSTANCE_ID and LBI.STARTER_ID = LUX.USER_ID(+) and LBI.EXECUTION_STATUS = LBSC.STATUS_ID and lt.status not in (32) and lt.activity_task_type = 1 and (LT.EXECUTION_STATUS != 1 or LT.EXECUTION_STATUS is null) and (UPPER(LUX.USER_NAME) like ? or UPPER(LT.SUBJECT) like ? or UPPER(LT.ACTIVITY_NAME) like ? or LT.TASK_ID = ? or LT.BPD_INSTANCE_ID = ? or UPPER(lp.name) like ? or UPPER(lugx.description) like ? or UPPER(LBI.INSTANCE_NAME) like ? or UPPER(LBI.BPD_NAME) like ? or LBI.BPD_REF = ? or UPPER(lbsc.name) like ?) and lbsc.NAME = 'Active' order by LBI.BPD_REF
